- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about large vocabulary continuous speech recognition using neural network models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses a new approach for training neural network models. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the implementation of the proposed method in a training system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper is about training neural network models for speech recognition. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possibility as the paper discusses the use of neural network models for speech recognition.
